{"tid":149832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登公投 - 胡官係唔係鬼","createTime":"2017-03-09T14:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T16:43:59.000Z","uid":7369,"like":10,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38042f528cf476a4519ead51db11c04a6b91deef","tid":149832,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係鬼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬼你老母"},{"pid":"1912bc2b51a56c43834e2105895a48b2fba5cdc6","tid":149832,"uid":8724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:15:41.000Z","msg":"品客都係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a7df2976ae5a51d2b2be938d3dfc74fea72e65","tid":149832,"uid":3232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:22:07.000Z","msg":"全部都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711c7ba5486cab9fb6801fef1f39dd5e6ee3af4d","tid":149832,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:37:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【特首跑馬仔】胡國興籲泛民分散投資　郭榮鏗：沒有分票的條件</span><br />\n<br />\n特首候選人胡國興今早出席電台節目時，稱民主派選委應「分散投資」，分別給予2名候選人各160票，藉以從第一輪投票結果掌握建制派的選票流向，到第二輪投票時，再投給其中一名取得較多建制票的候選人。<br />\n<br />\n負責協調民主派選委的「專業議政」立法會議員郭榮鏗今午回應說法，強調民主派選委「沒有分票的條件，只有團結的需要」，認為民主派選委須團結，投票予一名候選人。他稱，民主派在選委會屬少數，若再不團結，便沒有可能發揮作用。<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗稱，希望胡國興認清形勢，「看清楚自己站的位置」。問及胡國興的說法，會否令民主派減低投票予他的意欲，郭榮鏗稱「不會講到咁遠」，但重申很多民主派選委不認同胡的意見。郭榮鏗又認為，「游離票」是在林鄭月娥一方，而非在曾俊華一方。<br />\n<br />\n至於投票取向，郭榮鏗稱民主派選委會在今月20日開會討論。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170309/s00001/1489050613141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170309%2Fs00001%2F1489050613141&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=72d84179\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170309%2Fs00001%2F1489050613141&h=14300059\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170309/s00001/1489050613141</a></span>"},{"pid":"4034b0de8132fbc25ccf5b0bf3e4874fd88d7ee7","tid":149832,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}